{"tid":2505058,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日經民調：74%日本民眾支持參與追求台海穩定","createTime":"2021-04-26T10:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T13:09:34.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"333b1119e6ea1ef136896eca0f9f7234323109ec","tid":2505058,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:29:09.000Z","msg":"日經民調：74%日本民眾支持參與追求台海穩定<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/5413573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F5413573&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B69EgU5aikFnqk5iyu2dsMw0%3D&h=4d9f97fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/5413573</a><br />\n<br />\n日經亞洲評論報導，根據日本經濟新聞和東京電視台進行的一項民調，日本大多數民眾支持政府參與追求台灣海峽的和平穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">調查緣起是美國總統拜登和日本首相菅義偉4月16日峰會後發表聯合公報，同意台灣海峽和平穩定的重要性，這也是1969年以來美日聯合聲明首次提到台灣。<br />\n<br />\n根據民調，74%的受訪者支持日本參與追求台灣海峽的穩定，13%反對。每個年齡層支持參與的比率都高於反對，逾60歲民眾有74%支持，40-50歲間有80%支持，18-39歲之間是69%。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n這次民調於上周五到周日之間，對18歲以上民眾進行電話訪調，有效樣本為1,026份。"},{"pid":"3aacf0124bce4a81ba20f7b76e5d1e543416cc8e","tid":2505058,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T12:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ebfd94df19f9cb66abdc7598a5a541cbe6ea1c","tid":2505058,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T12:57:02.000Z","msg":"支joke<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6134cdb3cd3ee1f73b656c0abbcedc138e106679","tid":2505058,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:09:34.000Z","msg":"反對嗰啲係支持台灣武統支那？"}]}